      "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body": "Thanks for the report. This looks like a spurious test failure. This is from a test added in https://github.com/bitcoin-core/libmultiprocess/pull/237/changes/5205a87cd90e23f5aa2ae8503213dc90bd557bfd (https://github.com/bitcoin-core/libmultiprocess/pull/237, #34363) which has a short [1 second](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/8b461c530e95d3a09bce0d157873728c8be5fd22/src/ipc/libmultiprocess/test/mp/test/spawn_tests.cpp#L99) timeout which should be increased to be more reliable in CI.",
